{
  "stem": "14060.7",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were making marks in the sand with our finger.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And first, we made a, a, a, [INAUDIBLE] a swastika.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we put a cross over it-- bad, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I couldn't speak Russian, he couldn't speak at all.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then we made a hammer and sickle-- mm, well.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this went on for about a half an hour or so.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, it was just whiling away time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And suddenly, the guy takes out a [? seder. ?] Now, [? seder ?] was by sentence of death if they caught you with it.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he gave it to me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was like as if I tell you that you have suddenly been given a jumbo jet, you know?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was out of the world.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I put it in my pocket.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a small [? seder. ?] So eventually, I took that with me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They never found it on me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was no body searches, if you know what I mean.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were not taken regularly for disinfection or, or, or change of clothing or anything.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So nobody bothered, really.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But anyway, we got into the block 23.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I must say that, maybe understandably, the main part of the occupants, of the other inmates, were young or not so young-- some of them boys-- who originated from the Warsaw ghetto and jumped off the trains to Treblinka but were caught later on.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they were obviously not taken to Treblinka.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Maybe by the time it was 1944, and the Warsaw ghetto was liquidated already two, two and a half years earlier, and came to Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Now I understand-- and I'm not having any arguments about it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because, you see, what one should not forget-- there was not an absolute harmony in these camps.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
